{"word":"Prisoners","slug":"prisoners","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Prisoners</b> Joseph<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=39&verse=23'>Gen 39:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=40'>Gen 40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=41&verse=44'>Gen 41:44</a><br/> Jeremiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=38&verse=28'>Jer 38:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=39&verse=14'>Jer 39:14</a><br/> John the Baptist<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=11&verse=2'>Mat 11:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=14&verse=12'>Mat 14:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=6&verse=17'>Mar 6:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=3&verse=20'>Luk 3:20</a><br/> Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=75'>Mat 26:75</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=27'>Mat 27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=14&verse=72'>Mar 14:72</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=15'>Mar 15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=22&verse=71'>Luk 22:71</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=23'>Luk 23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=18&verse=40'>Joh 18:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=19'>Joh 19</a><br/> Apostles<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=5&verse=42'>Act 5:42</a><br/> Peter<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=12&verse=19'>Act 12:19</a><br/> Paul<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=16&verse=40'>Act 16:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=21&verse=40'>Act 21:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=22'>Act 22</a><br/> Silas<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=16&verse=40'>Act 16:40</a><br/> Required to labor<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=16&verse=21'>Jdg 16:21</a><br/> Kept on bread and water of affliction<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=22&verse=27'>1Ki 22:27</a><br/> Kept in chains<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=12&verse=6'>Act 12:6</a><br/> Kept in stocks<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=7&verse=22'>Pro 7:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=29&verse=26'>Jer 29:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=16&verse=24'>Act 16:24</a><br/> Confined in:<br/> - Court of the palace<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=32&verse=2'>Jer 32:2</a> <br/> - House of the scribe<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=37&verse=15'>Jer 37:15</a> <br/> - House of captain of the guard<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=40&verse=3'>Gen 40:3</a> <br/> Visited by friends<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=11&verse=2'>Mat 11:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=24&verse=23'>Act 24:23</a><br/> Bound to soldiers<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=12&verse=7'>Act 12:7</a><br/> Severe hardships of, mitigated<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=37&verse=21'>Jer 37:21</a><br/> Cruelty to<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=38&verse=6'>Jer 38:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=25&chapter=3&verse=54'>Lam 3:54</a><br/><a href='S:Captive'>Captive</a> <br/> Keepers responsible for<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=12&verse=19'>Act 12:19</a><br/> Tortured to extort self-criminating testimony<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=22&verse=24'>Act 22:24</a><br/> Scourged<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=27&verse=26'>Mat 27:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=15&verse=15'>Mar 15:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=16&verse=23'>Act 16:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=16&verse=33'>Act 16:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=6&verse=5'>2Co 6:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=11&verse=24'>2Co 11:24</a><br/> Permitted to make defense<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=24&verse=10'>Act 24:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=25&verse=8'>Act 25:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=25&verse=16'>Act 25:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=26&verse=1'>Act 26:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=55&chapter=4&verse=16'>2Ti 4:16</a><br/> Kindness to:<br/> - By the prison keeper to Jeremiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=38&verse=28'>Jer 38:28</a> <br/> - By Philippian jailer to Paul<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=16&verse=33'>Act 16:33</a> <br/> - By Felix<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=24&verse=23'>Act 24:23</a> <br/> - By Julius, the centurion<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=27&verse=1'>Act 27:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=27&verse=3'>Act 27:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=28&verse=16'>Act 28:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=28&verse=31'>Act 28:31</a> <br/> To be visited and ministered to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=25&verse=46'>Mat 25:46</a><br/> Released at feasts<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=27&verse=17'>Mat 27:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=15&verse=6'>Mar 15:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=23&verse=17'>Luk 23:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=18&verse=39'>Joh 18:39</a><br/> Of war:<br/> - Put to death<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=10&verse=27'>Jos 10:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=15&verse=33'>1Sa 15:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=27&verse=11'>1Sa 27:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=12&verse=31'>2Sa 12:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=25&verse=7'>2Ki 25:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=20&verse=3'>1Ch 20:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=13&verse=16'>Hos 13:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=1&verse=13'>Amo 1:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=25&chapter=3&verse=34'>Lam 3:34</a> <br/> - Put to death by divine command<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=31&verse=9'>Num 31:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=31&verse=17'>Num 31:17</a> <br/> - Thumbs and toes cut off<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=1&verse=7'>Jdg 1:7</a> <br/> - Blinded<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=25&verse=7'>2Ki 25:7</a><br/><a href='S:Captive'>Captive</a> <br/> - Consolations for<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=69&verse=33'>Psa 69:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=79&verse=11'>Psa 79:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=102&verse=20'>Psa 102:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=146&verse=7'>Psa 146:7</a><br/><a href=